{"tid":1487064,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中共維穩：今星期開始吹緊咩風, 打緊咩主意?","createTime":"2019-08-19T06:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T14:18:51.000Z","uid":282490,"like":185,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"9f492c5e8c111284b4836639a9c928910e251760","tid":1487064,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SPbrrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SPbrrO.jpg&h=a2bfb091&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中共打壓：吹緊咩風, 打緊咩主意?<br />\n一張藍尸圖睇哂<br />\n<br />\n我地都CONNECT左和+勇, 佢地今日先動員到黎玩分化<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">811臥底事件 + 和理非170萬遊行 + 放班生蕃小粉紅入黎屌勇武 = 打壓新方針</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n其實都係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">舖墊緊一個局：就係和理非同勇武互鬥 + 捉鬼</span></strong><br />\n我地仲未connect 哂架, 尋日幾多post 屌人留, 就有幾多熱衷捉鬼既同路人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">班藍尸做緊乜? 就係要同我地既和理非玩埋堆! </span><br />\n大家都係so call 討厭暴力, 所以佢地先咁大諗頭想搶人<br />\n<br />\n喺我地日後所有升級行動果陣, 各位香港人，可以應承一班較強行動力既手足(舊稱勇武)：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放核彈都唔割嗎？<br />\n<br />\n可以承諾唔屌前線手足嗎？<br />\n可以做到強大back up 嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"b7004cfd4639ad9c1ff7ce4921de14e3a908a84f","tid":1487064,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:03:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>P牌推唔郁</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n[細思極恐] 懷疑中共策劃緊另一場陰謀，已經成功瓦解緊成場運動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dGzpHS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dGzpHS</a>"},{"pid":"849adb67f989ccba810b59f81caf7a860832f7ed","tid":1487064,"uid":150544,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:04:38.000Z","msg":"中共最怕兩樣野<br />\n前線差佬變節<br />\n文宣大陸起義<br />\n